Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FREESTANDING BUILDING WITH OUTSTANDING DEVELOPMENT POTENTIAL

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Victorian Health, Aged & Child Care are delighted to present for sale 120 Thames Street, Box Hill.

This outstanding freestanding three (3) level premium healthcare opportunity is directly opposite Box Hill Hospital Eastern Health and nearby a variety of medical and allied health specialists.

The rarity to acquire a brand new, highly prominent, immaculately appointed freestanding building situated within Melbourne’s identified developing health and education precinct is not to be underestimated, not to mention the fact that this property boasts:

Freestanding 3 level building offering flexibility to occupy or generate strong holding income

Premium 1690 sqm* medical complex with a permit for 20 practitioners

Situated on a substantial site of 903sqm* which includes basement parking for 53 vehicles

Potential fully leased income estimated at $650,000pa*

Highly flexible floor plates allowing separate and multiple tenancies

An outstanding location close to Box Hill’s transport hub including Box Hill Train Station and Bus Interchange (10min walk), #109 tram to Port Melbourne (5min walk) and Eastern Freeway (1.8km*)
